verbose_text: To confirm the differential C19MC miRNA expression identified by real-time PCR based array assay, we investigated the expression of miR-517a-3p and miR-518b in the pNK cells at different time points of pregnancy by RT-qPCR (XREF_FIG) as these miRNAs were included in the 25 upregulated miRNAs of the third-trimester pNK cells.
